        Gingko biloba is an antioxidant-rich herb of Chinese origin that is used to enhance brain health and preserve memory. Most supplements are made using leaf extract, but some are made from the seeds of the plant. Gingko biloba increases blood flow to the brain.<br>
        </p>
    </article>    
